# Leadsy Application Specification

## 1. Purpose

Build a web-based **Leadsy application** that helps users identify potential business leads based on geographic area, product relevance, and AI-assisted qualification.

The system should support:

* Lead discovery from map-based search areas
* AI-assisted product-to-market matching
* Heatmap visualization for lead concentration
* Lead enrichment and deduplication
* Lead pipeline/funnel management
* WhatsApp-based follow-up
* Enterprise-grade governance, auditability, and access control

---

## 2. Business Objective

The application is intended to help commercial, presales, partnership, and business development teams:

* Discover high-potential companies within target locations
* Match the right product/use case to the right market segment
* Enrich leads with company and contact details
* Avoid duplicate lead creation
* Push qualified leads into a structured funnel
* Accelerate first outreach through WhatsApp
* Maintain governance, traceability, and controlled access

