## 12. Final Recommendation

The application should not be positioned as a simple lead scraper.
It should be designed as a **geo-intelligence + AI-assisted lead qualification + funnel orchestration platform** with proper governance.

With the addition of AI Provider & Model Management, the system becomes:

* Vendor-agnostic
* Scalable across multiple AI providers
* Governed and auditable
* Ready for enterprise deployment and cost control

This positioning makes it more scalable, more enterprise-ready, and more defensible from a product, security, and operational standpoint.

